      • Field

        public Field()
        Default constructor, fieldID, fieldNumber, xCoord, width, and projectID to -1 and all String values to "New" and their names, except for helpHTML, which is set to "/" and knownData, which is set to null.

      • Field

        public Field(int fieldID,
     int fieldNumber,
     int xCoord,
     int width,
     java.lang.String helpHTML,
     java.lang.String knownData,
     java.lang.String projectID)
        Parameters:
        fieldID - The unique ID assigned to each Field in the database
        fieldNumber - The order in which this Field appears in Project
        xCoord - The xCoordinate of this Field in each Record
        width - The width in pixels of this Field on the image
        helpHTML - The path of the helpfile for this project relative from the XML file
        knownData - This variable is optional, and indicates the location of a textfile with information already known about this Field
        projectID - The unique ID of the linked project
